snippet.title: Still Wakes the Deep - Trailer | PC Gaming Show 2024
snippet.description:
Don't miss the suspenseful Still Wakes the Deep trailer for the upcoming first-person narrative horror game from developer The Chinese Room, the creators of Everybody’s Gone to the Rapture and Dear Esther.

Still Wake the Deep is coming to PC, PS5, and Xbox Series X/S on June 18, 2024.

#IGN #Gaming #StillWakestheDeep
